title: What happened to YouTuber Jacob Chibi Reviews Seibers after heartfelt message made fans fear for his life
summary_full: Jacob “Chibi Reviews” Seibers worried fans after posting “I wanna die” on February 11, 2026. He later revealed he had a mental breakdown after discovering his fiancée cheated with his best friend. Police found him near a lake and took him to the hospital. In a YouTube video titled “i lost everything,” he thanked friends who helped save him.
